data.description:
*5.25% Interest Rate + $1,000 lender credit with preferred lender* Welcome to your future dream home in an idyllic neighborhood! This property offers a harmonious blend of modern sophistication and classic charm. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautifully updated flooring that extends throughout the home, setting the tone for a fresh and welcoming atmosphere.

The newly remodeled kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting pristine countertops, custom cabinets, and top-of-the-line appliances. The spacious space is the perfect centerpiece for family gatherings and entertaining, making this kitchen the heart of your home.

A versatile office or nursery, with elegant French doors, adds to the home's adaptability, providing a tranquil workspace or space for a growing family. The interior has been adorned with fresh paint, offering a blank canvas for your unique decorating style.

Outside, a generously sized fenced backyard beckons, offering a secure haven for kids and pets and an ideal backdrop for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. The neighborhood is a true gem, with friendly neighbors and well-kept streets creating a picturesque setting.

For those who enjoy an active lifestyle, the convenience of being within walking distance of the pool and recreational facility means you can make the most of your leisure time. This remarkable property is your chance to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and community. Don't let it slip away – schedule a viewing today and make it yours!
